Text: LufkinJpst On May th a lufkin Industrial market will go down by We are going to move this sale to Lyondell meter The sales price will remain at Index minus The sale will remain at Lyondell for approximately weeks Since the screen has fallen about this should be a good thing for us and a very nice thing for Entex to do for us Thanks Janet
